# $Id$

HUMAN.R a Rails pet-project
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

What:

  Human Resources Rails Pet-Project, somehow based on 
  "HR Schema on Rails" by by Casimir Saternos published in 
  June 2006 at Oracle(http://www.oracle.com/technology/pub/articles/saternos-rails.html).

Preq:

  Ruby (1.8.4)
  Rails (1.1.4)
  Database server supported by Rails

Install:

  $ cp config/database.yml.sample config/database.yml
edit config/database.yml to match your database connection settings.
  $ rake migrate
  $ script/server

Questions:

  aurelian[at]locknet[dot]ro

